<plot>Borrah Minevitch and His Harmonica Rascals, including Leo Diamond, join together in some virtuoso harmonica playing of a wide style of songs and music, including "Always in My Heart, " Bugle Call Rag", Cole Porter's "Begin the Beguine" and "Columbia, Gem of the Ocean." Warner's re-issued it a second time shortly after Minevitch's death.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?080055</url></doc>
